  "title": "⭐ Urgent Hiring! Junior Brand Ambassador",
  "description": "<p> Ready to Sell Smarter, Market Louder & Grow Faster?</p><p>Are you done with boring jobs that don’t get you or your vibe?</p><p>Want to build your career in a space that values creativity, strategy, and RESULTS?</p><p>We’re hiring Sales & Marketing Trailblazers </p><p>Whether you're fresh outta uni, a self-taught whiz, or already crushing it in your side hustle — we see you.</p><p>What you’ll do:</p><p> Create campaigns that actually convert</p><p> Own your pipeline (and your growth)</p><p> Connect with real people, not just leads</p><p> Shape how the brand speaks and shows up online</p><p>What we’re looking for:</p><p> Social-savvy, trend-aware thinkers</p><p> Growth mindset (and meme fluency helps too)</p><p> Hungry to learn, unafraid to test ideas</p><p> Can pitch, persuade, and pivot when needed</p><p>What’s in it for you:</p><p> Real responsibility from Day 1</p><p> Mentorship & skill-building (minus the buzzwords)</p><p> Work that actually gets seen</p><p> A team that values your ideas, not just your output</p><p>[Location] | </p><p> Entry-mid level |  Full-time</p><p> Slide into our DMs, drop us your CV, or show us your portfolio.</p><p>We're not just hiring — we’re building something. Want in?</p><p>#MarketingJobs #SalesSquad #NowHiring #JoinUs\n\n</p>",
